^^WI   }
^^WI  }
^^WI  @ 1,2 GRID GRR NROWS=5 NCOLS=3
^^WI  {
^^WI   @ 2,2 BUTTON BOK '&OK' DEFAULT
^^WI   @ 4,2 BUTTON BXX '&Cancel'
^^WI  }
^^WI }
^^WI SHOW
^^CR
%%
% CLEAR
